link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..422
formula: G.f.: (1 - 1728/j)^(1/2), where j is the j-function.
a(n) ~ (-1)^n * c * exp(Pi*sqrt(3)*n) * sqrt(n), where c = 32*sqrt(2) * Pi^(11/2) / Gamma(1/3)^9. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Mar 04 2018
